也没多想，就买了酒和烧烤带回家陪她。\n今天上午，刚到公司，我老婆突然跟我说有事要和我讲。说有点严重。然后聊下来我才知道，老丈人背着所有人借了网贷。但是具体不肯透露借了多少钱。我老婆上午从别人那里了解了一下，还借了朋友的钱。另外年初又自己自作主张换了车，也是借钱换的。\n我老婆现在不知道该怎么办。\n我因为和她父母关系一般，目前情绪没有太多的波动。\n目前我还没有买房，孩子刚上小学。我个人是不愿意帮忙还钱的。但是钱在老婆手上管着。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/trl5xsF.jpeg\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://i.imgur.com/trl5xsF.jpeg</a></p>\n", "last_modified": 1758267366, "replies": 229, "id": 1160533}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c9f0/f895/8_large.png?m=1630643991", "name": "iphone", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c9f0/f895/8_normal.png?m=1630643991", "title": "iPhone", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/iphone", "topics": 12442, "footer": "这里绝不讨论如何获得 iPhone 盗版软件、iTunes 黑卡之类。", "header": "Say hello to the future.", "title_alternative": "iPhone", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c9f0/f895/8_mini.png?m=1630643991", "stars": 3540, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 8, "parent_node_name": "apple"}, "member": {"id": 308169, "username": "fingers", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/fingers", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/3cde/3180/308169_mini.png?m=1757692723", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/3cde/3180/308169_normal.png?m=1757692723", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/3cde/3180/308169_large.png?m=1757692723", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/3cde/3180/308169_xlarge.png?m=1757692723", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/3cde/3180/308169_xxlarge.png?m=1757692723", "avatar_xxxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/3cde/3180/308169_xxxlarge.png?m=1757692723", "created": 1523523848, "last_modified": 1757692723, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "coolmint", "last_touched": 1758291210, "title": "17pro 貌似发烫挺严重的啊", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1160427", "created": 1758250384, "deleted": 0, "content": "目前还在同步数据中，14pro 没有烫的感觉，17pro 已经烫到不想用手拿了。", "content_rendered": "<